            "data_source": "Firmware",
            "data_component": "Firmware Modification",
            "description": "Monitor for changes made to firmware. Dump and inspect BIOS images on vulnerable systems and compare against known good images. Analyze differences to determine if malicious changes have occurred. Log attempts to read/write to BIOS and compare against known patching behavior. EFI modules can be collected and compared against a known-clean list of EFI executable binaries to detect potentially malicious modules. The CHIPSEC framework can be used for analysis to determine if firmware modifications have been performed.",
